Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.92,0:00:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Milza's Dartanian forces\Nhave safely joined ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.17,0:00:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I've received word that Lady Ururika's\Nfleet will be arriving soon at Castle Unicorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.76,0:00:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.40,0:00:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My cousin...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.53,0:00:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The true battle is only about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.97,0:00:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.39,0:01:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Nordic fleet,\Nconquerors of the Northern Seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.54,0:02:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting, Big Sister Marrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.04,0:02:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let the revelry begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.28,0:03:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How did the Nordic fleet get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me they actually came\Nhalfway around the continent?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The soldiers could've made it here on foot,\Nthen built the ships here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.33,0:03:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This spells defeat for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.59,0:03:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all the battles it's been through,\Nour navy's taken some serious hits.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.38,0:03:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And Lady Edokia's Palace of the Sea\Nwon't hold up for long against that giant fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.72,0:03:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Waldlind will be acting in concert with Nord,\Nso they're sure to make a move this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.02,0:03:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If they attack us from both land and sea,\Nthe castle won't last for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.49,0:04:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, how shall we lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.86,0:04:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can't surrender without\Nputting up a fight, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.12,0:04:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to prepare for battle now,\Nand take command at the palace gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.29,0:04:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What shall we tell the Lords in the vicinity?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.13,0:04:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have them decide for themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.75,0:04:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll thank them for all their help till now,\Nand apologize for the casualties they suffered.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.51,0:04:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And what of the Lords serving you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.39,0:04:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I'll catch hell\Nif I order them to surrender?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.52,0:04:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure about them giving you hell,\Nbut I don't see them complying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.98,0:04:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll leave the phrasing up to you, Laura.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.15,0:04:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to stay here,\Nand contact the princes and Lords.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.37,0:04:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Understood?\N- Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.29,0:04:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Helga, take care of the wounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.54,0:04:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whether they be allies or enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.29,0:04:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It may sound contradictory,\Nbut that's also what war is all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:05:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.17,0:05:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To both of you, thank you for serving\Nthis Lustful Earl so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.05,0:05:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sincerely grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.18,0:05:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Villar...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.31,0:05:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,May you be victorious!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.06,0:05:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As for Siluca, give her this message.\N"Your advice turned out to be right."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.48,0:05:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Though I'm sure she already knew that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.44,0:05:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, Marrine was just that formidable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.28,0:05:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think I have a message for Theo, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.50,0:05:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Nords?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.17,0:05:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A massive fleet of more than 1,000 ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.59,0:05:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're riding the tide,\Nheading this way at top speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.50,0:05:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Joachim.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.30,0:05:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.16,0:06:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we've lost this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.91,0:06:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hear the earl himself is prepared for defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.37,0:06:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.87,0:06:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So Lord Villar's luck has finally run out, has it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.59,0:06:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've been apprehensive since hearing\Nthe verdict at the Lords' Congress.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.13,0:06:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There will be no escaping the Nords\Non this palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.26,0:06:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You must transfer to a smaller boat,\Nand flee this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.56,0:06:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All together?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.97,0:06:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No. Just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.14,0:06:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since we've all loved you equally,\Nwe'll go out as equals, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.02,0:06:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.65,0:06:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't survive without all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.78,0:06:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look after our children for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.76,0:07:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know, you don't have\Nto accompany me in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.06,0:07:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If it means being the last woman to stand\Nby the side of Villar, the Earl of Altirk,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.02,0:07:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I could want nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.32,0:07:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I really wanted you to find happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.70,0:07:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do I look unhappy to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.42,0:07:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd been afraid to love all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.64,0:07:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But now that it's come to this,\NI think I can forgive myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.15,0:08:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see now that life is worth risking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.90,0:08:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You could've risked it for so many other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.28,0:08:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently,\Nthey were all too insignificant for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.16,0:08:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You really are... eccentric.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.42,0:08:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,W-What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.26,0:08:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If the sun was out, I could use this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.78,0:08:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Altirk ships are sustaining heavy damages.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We must go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.80,0:09:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Waves, surge!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.14,0:09:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flames, explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.93,0:09:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flames! Expl-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.74,0:09:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Edo... kia...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.78,0:10:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.78,0:10:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who would've thought that Waldlind\Nwould be this aggressive?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.41,0:10:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all the damage the Earl of Altirk\Nwas able to inflict on the Alliance,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.29,0:10:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we squandered what time we had,\Ngiving them a chance to mount a comeback.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And now the Earl of Altirk himself is\Nthe first to be driven to the brink!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.38,0:10:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He has himself to blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.47,0:10:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Marrine Kreische spurned our offer of a truce\Nbecause she couldn't forgive Altirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.14,0:10:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand, it means the only person\Nthey hate is Villar Constance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.56,0:10:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Once they seize his Crest,\Nthey'll surely be willing to talk peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.11,0:10:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you mad? Or perhaps\Nyou have some kind of secret pact in play?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.44,0:10:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.57,0:10:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please, calm yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.62,0:11:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wish to save the Earl of Altirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.08,0:11:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Towards that end...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.12,0:11:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What if we recognize\Nthe Kreische family as emperors,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.92,0:11:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and all Union Lords\Nswear allegiance to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.63,0:11:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying we should surrender?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.84,0:11:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I believe we have no other option.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.18,0:11:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is commendable you feel that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.64,0:11:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However, the Alliance is poised to destroy\Nthe Union in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.77,0:11:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever conditions we propose,\Nit's unlikely their stance will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.44,0:11:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But we must save the Earl of Altirk\Nat any cost...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.94,0:11:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Castle Unicorn is surrounded on all sides.\NIt's too late to take action now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.41,0:11:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At this point, we should discuss how\Nto proceed after the earl's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.29,0:11:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know yet if it's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.70,0:11:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll invade the Alliance domains from the north.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we threaten from the rear,\NWaldlind just might retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.88,0:12:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why, Marrine?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.47,0:12:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't it you who said our marriage would\Nend the era of Chaos,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.56,0:12:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and bring peace to the Continent?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.94,0:12:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stand your ground!\NDon't think of retreating even a single step!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.54,0:12:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Advance!\NBreach the palace gates in one go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.56,0:12:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Nordic soldiers appear to have landed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.52,0:12:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's only a matter of time before they\Nbreach the seaward fortress and close in on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.86,0:13:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've ordered the gate soldiers to retreat,\Nand switch defense to inside the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.82,0:13:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.32,0:13:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go on our final rampage!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.58,0:13:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.33,0:13:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hellfire Margaret's final spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.09,0:13:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to show you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've been afraid to love.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.03,0:13:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For I did not want to lose the one I loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.51,0:14:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Be that as it may, you've offered me\Nthe greatest love of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.44,0:14:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All I ever wanted was to be by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.22,0:14:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?\NI thought I'd find the Lord here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.06,0:14:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Ururika, daughter of Erik,\Nthe Marquis of Nord. Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.35,0:15:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A mage under contract to Lord Villar,\NEarl of Altirk. Colleen Messala.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.77,0:15:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since the Lustful Earl is still alive,\Nhis contract with you is still valid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.91,0:15:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Which means I won't be\Nviolating the code if I kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.45,0:16:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Earl of Altirk shall be slain by Waldlind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.58,0:16:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grandfather Jurgen will have his revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.71,0:16:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.25,0:16:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Captain of the Guard Regiment!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.63,0:16:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Heavy crossbows at the ready!\NLoad the Crest Bullets!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.10,0:16:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.91,0:17:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,P-Prepare for the second volley!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.70,0:17:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.29,0:17:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Your Highness!\N- It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.46,0:17:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Villar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.01,0:17:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.77,0:17:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My Kreische blood and my Crest\Nare yours now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.65,0:17:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.07,0:17:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You should continue to follow\Nthe path you believe in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.74,0:18:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That said, I will still pray\Nfor you and Lord Alexis to be wed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.50,0:18:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since that's how I believe\Nyou'll find true happiness...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.22,0:18:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cousin of mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.23,0:18:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've abandoned any thought\Nof attaining happiness for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.17,0:18:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To repay Lord Villar,\Nwe must kill as many of the enemy as we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.01,0:19:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am the Mage Leader under contract\Nto Villar Constance, Earl of Altirk,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.39,0:19:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Laura Hardley.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.85,0:19:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This castle and throne\Nshall be relinquished to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.02,0:19:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it does not mean Altirk has been defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.86,0:20:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Lords of this domain\Nwill surely rise up against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.95,0:20:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Glory to Altirk!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.30,0:20:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Helga Piarosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.43,0:20:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Will you allow me to\Ncontinue tending to the wounded?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.80,0:20:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you bring in your own wounded,\NI will treat them equally.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.81,0:20:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.31,0:20:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.49,0:20:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I shall now yield this castle\Nand Villar's Crest to you, Lord Milza.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.07,0:20:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to conquer Altirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.20,0:20:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.10,0:21:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.56,0:21:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Those who lack ambition are eliminated,\Nand the weak are destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.98,0:21:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Such an era has finally arrived.
